data.description: Welcome home!  This charming rancher boasts a spacious fenced backyard with ample space for gardening, play, and gatherings. The interior features 3 bedrooms and 1 bath, providing the perfect blend of functionality and comfort.  This home is thoughtfully situated in Northampton and just minutes away from entertainment and shopping.  Experience the joy of single-level living combined with the allure of a sizable backyard!
